Run the provider-side server.

Fronts an OpenAI-compatible upstream behind SomaPay-authorized `/v1/chat/completions`. Backends today: openrouter, vast.

Usage: soma inference serve [OPTIONS] --config <CONFIG>

Options:
      --config <CONFIG>
          Path to the provider TOML config

      --address <ADDRESS>
          Address whose keypair signs the channel; defaults to the keystore's active address

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')

EXAMPLE:
    soma inference serve --config provider.toml
